ERisk ESSENTIALS --
What's New at ERisk.com, 1 June 2001

This week's Essentials is brought to you by The Risk Desk, the energy industry's newest and most widely read publication on risk management best practices and market trends...who says energy trading risk management has to be dull? Download a free issue of the monthly electronic publication at
